      "message": "AFAIK, the existing python implementation allows any step names as long as it\u0027s unique and not an empty string.\n\nThe field-description in the proto doesn\u0027t describe about the acceptable form of values, either.\nhttps://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/buildbucket/proto/step.proto;l\u003d28-35\n\nTherefore, all of the following step names are valid.\n- \"   \"\n- \" |   | \"\n- \"a|b||\"\n- \"|a|\"\n\nIs it intended?",
