        "id": 1147264
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-29T16:15:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "how about the character set?\ni.e.,\n\"a regex with [[:print:]]\" vs\nstrings.split() with checking the length and leading/trailing char of each segment\n\nShould we allow unicode?",
      "parentUuid": "096fa8bd_697dff07",
      "range": {
