    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "2c80c43a_2e061b48",
        "filename": "buildbucket/appengine/rpc/update_build.go",
        "patchSetId": 2
      },
      "lineNbr": 109,
      "author": {
        "id": 1003211
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-31T16:36:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "What\u0027s wrong with empty or whitespace step names? I would just allow every character except reserved separator |. And even then |\u0027s reservation is implicit, as in the current CL. If your step contains | it just assumes you referenced a non-existent parent... or maybe by coincidence you referenced a previous step, as long as it\u0027s documented who cares? Do steps starting with spaces break our services?",
      "parentUuid": "cc29359f_7f7d0511",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 107,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 109,
        "endChar": 3
      },
      "revId": "7f32c1bece230024c95f5f1807f1b97de47681bd",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "fa6aecf9_b99268f0",
        "filename": "buildbucket/appengine/rpc/update_build.go",
        "patchSetId": 2
      },
      "lineNbr": 109,
      "author": {
        "id": 1147264
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-31T19:58:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t have an objection for names with a leading/trailing whitespace char. However, it can be confusing if an empty space is allowed.\n\nAt https://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:appengine/cr-buildbucket/validation.py;l\u003d378-379, the validator validates the status and timestamps with the parent step. Therefore, it needs to find who the parent step is, but.\n\nQ. What\u0027s the parent of \"|\"? Does it have a parent?\nIf Yes, then the step itself is the parent and child?\nIf No, then what\u0027s the parent of \"a|\"?  it doesn\u0027t have a parent either?",
      "parentUuid": "2c80c43a_2e061b48",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 107,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 109,
        "endChar": 3
      },
      "revId": "7f32c1bece230024c95f5f1807f1b97de47681bd",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
